data.description: *SELLER WILL PAY $5,000 TOWARDS CLOSING PRICE*  This well-maintained 4-bedroom home is nestled on an oversized lot in Bon-Aire Subdivision in Hammond. This home features an open floor plan, recessed lighting, a wood-burning fireplace, beautiful laminate wood flooring, a wet bar with custom built-ins, and an oversized window in the dining area. The kitchen offers grey custom cabinetry, a pantry, an electric cooktop, stainless steel appliances, an island with a wood countertop, and a breakfast bar, perfect for casual dining. The rooms are all very spacious with abundant closet storage, and the master bath features double vanities, a large soaking tub, and a separate shower. You will love your evenings outdoors under the extended covered patio with views of your large backyard. Bon Aire Subdivision has a community pool. Call today for your private showing.
